<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

  <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Alata');

      body {
          font-family: 'Alata', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Calibri, sans-serif;
          height: 100%;
          box-sizing: border-box;
          padding: 40px 20px;
          font-size: 1.2em;
          color: whitesmoke;
          background-color: #181A1B;
          text-align: center;
      }

      button {
          font-family: 'Alata', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Calibri, sans-serif;
          padding: 5px 20px;
          font-size: 1em;
          border: 0;
          border-radius: 5px;
          text-align: center;
          vertical-align: middle;
          cursor: pointer;
      }

      button.sign-in, a.purge {
          font-size: 1em;
          border: 0;
          border-radius: 5px;
          text-align: center;
          vertical-align: middle;
          cursor: pointer;
          background-color: #006633;
      }


      .link-as-button {
          padding: 5px 20px;
          text-decoration: none;
          font-size: 1em;
          border: 0;
          border-radius: 5px;
          text-align: center;
          vertical-align: middle;
          color: whitesmoke;
      }

      .button-as-link {
          font-size: 0.8em;
          background: none;
          border: none;
          color: white;
          cursor: pointer;
          display: inline;
      }

      .button-as-link:hover {
          color: #3391FF;
          text-decoration: underline;
      }
  </style>
  <title>Purge your Twitter followers</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Hi, I'm Volgnie</h1>

Do you want <span style="color: #FF0066">fewer</span> Twitter followers? I can help you remove up to 1,000, based on the criteria you
pick.


<% if has_flash_error %>
  <br>
  <div>
    Error: <%= get_flash_error %>
  </div>
<% end %>

<br>
<br>

<div>
  <% if current_user %>
    <br>
    <div>
      <span style="font-size: medium">You're currently signed in as <b><%= current_user["username"] %>.</b></span>
      <br>
      <br>
      <a href="/purge/start" class="link-as-button purge">Start Purge</a>
      <br>
      <br>
    </div>
  <% else %>
    <form action="/auth/twitter" method="post">
      <input type="hidden" name="authenticity_token" value='<%= csrf_token %>'>

      <div>
        <button type="submit" class="sign-in">
          Sign in with Twitter â†’
        </button>
      </div>
    </form>
  <% end %>
</div>

<% if current_user %>
  <form action="/auth/twitter" method="post">
    <input type="hidden" name="authenticity_token" value='<%= csrf_token %>'>

    <button type="submit" class="button-as-link">
      Sign in as a different account
    </button>
  </form>
  <form action="/auth/logout" method="post">
    <input type="hidden" name="authenticity_token" value='<%= csrf_token %>'>
    <div>
      <button type="submit" class="button-as-link">Log out</button>
    </div>
  </form>
  </div>
<% end %>

</body>
</html>